name: Q&A from Seattle, Washington, USA
description:
Hello from Seattle, Washington, USA! I can't believe it! 25,000 subscribers. Wow! Thanks to each and every one of you. I recently asked for questions on my channel's community tab as well as on Instagram (@JebBrooks and @JebBrooksFlies). In this video, I've answered a handful of those questions. There were so many, maybe I'll do another of these videos.

Again, thank you so very much for your support. I have really enjoyed sharing some of my travels with you and I hope you'll consider telling your friends about it so we can continue to grow this community!

More about Bolivia:
https://greenergrass.com/un-bolivia-able/

For more trip reports, please subscribe to my channel!
https://www.youtube.com/jebbrooksflies

And for planes on Instragram:
https://www.instagram.com/jebbrooksflies/
